summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Dearborn Street from Sixth Avenue South to Rainier Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by grading & regrading under Ordinance No. 20981 creating Local Improvement District No. 2075 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
